resources.string: "kayan intanet na masarrafai, Chrome ke tafiyarwa"

"Ganin intanet na Android wani tsari ne da Chrome ke tafiyarwa da ke kyale masarrafan Android su bayyanar da kayan intanet. Wannan tsarin an riga an kafa shi a na\'urarka kuma a rika sabunta shi don tabbatar kana da mafi sabuntar bayanan tsaro da sauran kafafen da aka toshe."
